divs: Sighting Detailsgrandmas house playing. cousins saw the object at night sky.object had lights around it.it looked like a cornucopia shape.object landed at mine and set there for awhile then lifted off very slowly,it gradually blended with the night sky and disappeared. next object was a large flourescent rectangle hovering for quiet awhile. next object was a large flash like a lift off. culberson and hudspeth countys. at the time the military was doing somekind of maneuvers.
trends: There has been one other sighting in Van Horn
There were no other sightings in Van Horn on or around June 9th 1970
